# Use App Store Connect API Key for authentication (recommended)
# This avoids 2FA prompts during CI/CD
#
# To set up:
# 1. Go to App Store Connect → Users and Access → Integrations → App Store Connect API
# 2. Click "Generate API Key" (or use existing)
# 3. Download the .p8 file
# 4. Note the Key ID and Issuer ID
# 5. Run: fastlane fastlane-credentials add --username bobbytulsiani@gmail.com
#    OR set environment variables (see below)

